	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I made a suitable test ROM for you: <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=13264&amp;p=155593#p155593" class="postlink">here</a><br /><br />This test ROM lets you create a full screen of any color, and you can toggle all the emphasis bits. Should run on NTSC/PAL/whatever, it's very simple, no special hardware tricks.<br /><br />Don't worry about the greyscale toggle, all that does is force all colors to use column 0 of the palette, it doesn't produce any new colors.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
